The use of monotonic attribute functions also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (machine learning) as this is a common technique used in this field. Finally, the paper also deals with the issue of interpretability in deep models, which could suggest that it belongs to the sub-category of cs.CR (cryptography and security).
